Route22_Text_EarlyRivalIntro::
	.string "{RIVAL}: Hey! {PLAYER}!\p"
	.string "Heading to the SUPREME\n"
	.string "LICENSE GATE? Forget it!\p"
	.string "You barely have any BADGES,\n"
	.string "do you?\p"
	.string "The guard will not let you\n"
	.string "through without them.\p"
	.string "By the way, did your\n"
	.string "BRAINROT get stronger?$"

Route22_Text_EarlyRivalDefeat::
	.string "Awww!\n"
	.string "You just got lucky!$"

Route22_Text_EarlyRivalPostBattle::
	.string "I heard the Supreme License\n"
	.string "path is full of monsters.\p"
	.string "I will pass it before you.\p"
	.string "Stop dragging your feet!$"

Route22_Text_RivalShouldCatchSomeMons::
	.string "{RIVAL}: What? Why do I have\n"
	.string "two BRAINROTS?\p"
	.string "Because I actually catch them.\n"
	.string "Try it sometime!$"

Route22_Text_LateRivalIntro::
	.string "{RIVAL}: What? {PLAYER}!\n"
	.string "You made it here too?\p"
	.string "So you are aiming for the\n"
	.string "SUPREME LICENSE?\p"
	.string "You collected the BADGES?\n"
	.string "Fine. That is almost cool.\p"
	.string "I will beat you now as\n"
	.string "my warm-up. Come on!$"

Route22_Text_LateRivalDefeat::
	.string "What!?\p"
	.string "I was just careless!$"

Route22_Text_LateRivalPostBattle::
	.string "That warmed me up.\n"
	.string "I am ready for the gate.\p"
	.string "{PLAYER}, you still need\n"
	.string "practice. You know that.\p"
	.string "I am out of here.$"

Route22_Text_LateRivalVictory::
	.string "{RIVAL}: Hahaha! {PLAYER}!\n"
	.string "That is your best?\p"
	.string "Class S is still far above you.\n"
	.string "Go train more!$"

Route22_Text_LeagueGateSign::
	.string "SUPREME LICENSE ROAD\n"
	.string "Front Gate$"
